This is the working package to set up OSM Tile Server.
Its Installation is very easy.

Requirement: Ubuntu 10.04

1. Download meramap.deb package and Install it, It will install all the required software and dependency to set up Rendering Map Server.

2. Move to the newmap directory and run postinst script in the terminal, 
<pre>
./postinst
</pre>

3. This will generate a sample map at http://localhost/meramap
